#

Guacamole with Roasted Corn

25 min
$8
200 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerHealthyEasy

Description

A creamy and zesty guacamole paired with sweet roasted corn for a delightful twist.

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh cilantro: 1/4 cup
  • red onion: 1/4 cup, diced
  • tomato: 1, diced
  • corn kernels (fresh or frozen): 1 cup
  • salt: to taste
